<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<p>The dataset includes 308 national teams. For most of the games, the home team score is greater than the away team score. As some games could take place in a neutral location, we can ensure this hypothesis using the variable 'neutral'. We can also notice that the number of goals per match is pretty low (median of 1 for the away and the home team).</p>

