<div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class="prompt input_prompt">
</div>
<div class="inner_cell">
<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<p><b>Problematic :</b></p>
<p>During this study, we will try to predict the games issues which took place after 2015.</p>
<p>Before doing the study, we can notice that some teams names changed during the time due to the past events. We need to change the old names by the new names otherwise it will add too much bias in the data.</p>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="cell border-box-sizing code_cell rendered">
<div class="input">
<div class="prompt input_prompt">In&nbsp;[5]:</div>
<div class="inner_cell">
    <div class="input_area">
<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="n">name</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="s2">&quot;German DR&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&quot;Germany&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="s2">&quot;Czechoslovakia&quot;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&quot;Czech Republic&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="s1">&#39;Yugoslavia&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s1">&#39;Serbia&#39;</span><span class="p">,</span>
        <span class="s1">&#39;Yemen DPR&#39;</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s1">&#39;Yemen&#39;</span><span class="p">}</span>
<span class="n">name</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">&quot;&#39;</span><span class="si">{}</span><span class="s2">&#39;, &#39;</span><span class="si">{}</span><span class="s2">&#39;&quot;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">format</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">name</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">name</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">name</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">&quot;, &quot;</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">join</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">football</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s2">&quot;home_team&quot;</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">apply</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">&quot;DECODE(</span><span class="si">{}</span><span class="s2">, &quot;</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">name</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s2">&quot;, </span><span class="si">{}</span><span class="s2">)&quot;</span><span class="p">)</span>
