<h3 id="Teams-KPIs">Teams KPIs<a class="anchor-link" href="#Teams-KPIs">&#182;</a></h3><p>As the team is included in two variables (away_team and home_team), it is not easy to compute the new features. We need to duplicate the dataset to intervert the away team and the home team. As all the KPIs will be computed using a partition by the first team, we will not never use twice the same game.</p>

</div>
